        &lt;p&gt;
This is now done. See &lt;a class="missing changeset" title="No default repository defined"&gt;[1]&lt;/a&gt; for the deployment documentation and conventions.
CKAN checks the remote schema version on startup to see if it's compatible. See commits starting from 50285ef6.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
The migration work needed after releasing 1.5.1 is described in &lt;a class="closed ticket" href="http://localhost/ticket/1516" title="task: Update SOLR schema after 1.5.1 release and set up multicore SOLR instances ... (closed: fixed)"&gt;#1516&lt;/a&gt;.
